    <item>
      <title>特朗普冻结联邦土地和水域的可再生能源项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-freezes-renewable-projects-on-federal-lands-and-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府正在冻结在联邦土地和水域上开展风能和太阳能项目的授权，凸显出华盛顿的政策急剧转向青睐化石燃料而非可再生能源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-freezes-renewable-projects-on-federal-lands-and-waters</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 01:05:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽瓦克市长抨击 ICE 在突袭行动开始后拘留退伍军人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/newark-mayor-slams-ice-for-detaining-military-vet-as-raids-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽瓦克市市长和该选区的一名民主党女议员严厉谴责移民和海关执法局，称执法人员在没有出示搜查令的情况下突击检查了新泽西州的一家企业并拘留了无证居民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/newark-mayor-slams-ice-for-detaining-military-vet-as-raids-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:45:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本石破茂面临预算紧缩问题，并会见特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/japan-s-ishiba-faces-crunch-over-budget-meeting-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相石破茂将于周五召开议会，以期为他的少数派政府争取支持，同时他计划通过创纪录的 115.5 万亿日元（7380 亿美元）年度预算，并处理与美国新政府的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/japan-s-ishiba-faces-crunch-over-budget-meeting-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
